ina at Charlotte</em> <img src=\"https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f4f9.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Lecture Videos\" title=\"Lecture Videos\"> <img src=\"https://assets-cdn.github.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f4da.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" alt=\"Readings\" title=\"Readings\">\n<ul>\n<li>Introduction to designing microcontroller-based embedded computer systems using assembly and C programs. Examination of Real-time Operating Systems and their impact on performance. Computer engineering applications will be emphasized.</li>\n<li>The goal of this course is to solidify and build upon a student’s knowledge of computer organization by presenting hands-on experience with microcontrollers. Students will also examine a few sensors that are used in commercial and medical products and learn how to interface them in a microcontroller system.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPIqCiMhcdO5gxLJWt_hY5CPMzqg75IU5\">Lecture Videos</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://webpages.uncc.edu/~jmconrad/EducationalMaterials/index.html\">Lecture Notes</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-15T19:10:38.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"MunGell/awesome-for-beginners","categoryHTML":"<h2>Ruby</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rails/rails/labels/good%20first%20issue\">Ruby on Rails</a> <em>(label: good first issue)</em> <br> Ruby on Rails (Rails) is an open source web application framework written in Ruby.</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-15T18:44:37.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"MunGell/awesome-for-beginners","categoryHTML":"<h2>Python</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/wemake-services/wemake-python-styleguide/labels/level%3Astarter\">wemake-python-styleguide</a> <em>(label: level:starter)</em> <br> The strictest and most opinionated python linter ever!</li>","updatedAt":"2019-10-15T18:43:17.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"akullpp/awesome-java","categoryHTML":"<h2>Projects</h2><h3>Introspection</h3>","itemHTML":"<l